2006 Knysna SA

Ndidi on the day of his mothers funeral
Reading and Writing is Life
I read the words I want to hold
to keep inside of me
the dreams I imagine
And write the words I want to unchain
to release
the reality reaped, sown 
I read to take life in
and write to let it go

Midnight Musings by 
Tammi Brown Keech
2022
